snippet.title: Star Fox for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Worst Defender rip-off ever...or...at least on the Atari 2600.

It is monotonous, there is no life counter, you can destroy enemies if you crash into them and you won't get destroyed and there is no score board.

Also there is this quite annoying background sound.

And because of this game we Europeans and Australians have "StarWing" instead of "StarFox". Well, I could care less (or even not at all) if this game here would be good, or at least mediocre...BUT IT'S FRIGGIN' TERRIBLE!!!

This is just another lousy Mythicon fail to avoid...
